reviewText: Bought for my 23 month old grandson. He loves it. Every morning I hear dinosaurs, dinosaurs tv. Thank you
My Grandson LOVES these videos.  He just turned 2 yrs, and has been obsessed with Dinosaur Train since he was 6 months old.
My grans on loves these series

This DVD contains eight episodes from the Dinosaur Train cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Turtle and Theropod Race
2. Hungry, Hungry Carnivores
3. Air Obstacle Race
4. King & Crystal Live!
5. Air, Water and Land
6. Desert Day and Night
7. Ultimate Face-off
8. Back in Time
Purchased this for my 2 year old grandson and he loves it.
all nice stories with interesting characters that is easy to relate. my 5yr old enjoyed this as much as all the other Dino Train DVDs
